           <h1>BOBA TEA</h1>
      <p>Pink boba tea is a delightful twist on the classic bubble tea, known for its vibrant hue and sweet, creamy flavor.</p>
         <ol>☁️Typically made with a blend of fruit-infused milk or strawberry-flavored tea, it's paired with chewy tapioca pearls that add a fun texture to every sip. The eye-catching pink color makes it a favorite for social media snaps, while its refreshing taste keeps fans coming back for more.</ol> 
        <ol>Whether served iced or blended, pink boba tea is both a treat for the palate and a feast for the eyes.</ol>
        
